<br>
The policy i go by is pretty simple<br>
1. Only p/p if I am ML and I make sure the grp knows im doing it.<br>
2. Never p/p in guild grps or on ANY raids<br>
<br>
Pretty easy..not saying you should abide by it just that i do <p>-Myrdden

